/*************************************************************************
* ToyBox Demo Program resource file.
*
* Note: The BMP files used by this program are named using the
*       convention BALLx-y.BMP, with the 'x' character indicating which
*       'group' of objects the bitmap is used with, while the 'y'
*               character indicates which animation 'frame' of the 'group' the
*               object belongs is.
*
* 08/08/95 - Original Version, Dan Mendrala, IBM Corporation, 1995.
*
*************************************************************************/

